title: Dean of SNU Business School Acknowledges the Need to Integrate Engineering into the Business Degree ...
text: ( Source : Seoul National University ) Professor NAM Ick-Hyun, Dean of SNU Business School Seoul National University Business School declared that it would cultivate future business managers who are familiar with the engineering sector.
